  </tr>
</table>

\htmlonly </blockquote> \endhtmlonly




<tt>while \em cond { \em statements }</tt>

\htmlonly <blockquote> \endhtmlonly

Repeatedly execute \em statements while \em cond remains true upon entry. (See the description of \em cond expression syntax under if above).

