    <td><code> :\\\\ </code></td>
	<td>Convert all forward slashes (/) to backslashes (\\).</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><code> :I=<i>regex</i> </code></td>
	<td>Include all list items matching <i>regex</i>.  Remove everything else.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
